<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/alohacc/6635509529/" title="Flickr 上 aloooooooooooha 的 14"><img src="http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7153/6635509529_3e1da0e075.jpg" width="500" height="375" alt="14"></a></p>

